"{\"content\":{\"body\":\"12月30日消息，墨西哥政府总统府的官方账户宣布，墨西哥央行已计划在2024年前发行[数字货币](https://www.bitcoin86.com/)（CBDC）。墨西哥央行表示：“这些新技术和下一代支付基础设施极为重要，是推进该国金融包容性的极具价值的选择。”\",\"timestamp\":1640924345,\"title\":\"墨西哥央行计划于2024年前发行央行数字货币\"},\"digest\":\"lZZpyIe-NUfc94xxS5LsPXYRb0KCK7u3mE5MUigEFLQ\",\"authorship\":{\"contributor\":\"0xd44601c137bAf5E31eA098da4D0F38c54253c763\",\"signingKey\":\"{\\\"crv\\\":\\\"P-256\\\",\\\"ext\\\":true,\\\"key_ops\\\":[\\\"verify\\\"],\\\"kty\\\":\\\"EC\\\",\\\"x\\\":\\\"u1VTImaW42qZKYpTJCQc4JA6fFXOaU2iLQWK3ZuKlgs\\\",\\\"y\\\":\\\"cuS7q84y97hQVjZ8AhvNSlQ0X71TfqSzMcaGIVqzLDo\\\"}\",\"signature\":\"JOuw1EQUyFfj5wRAvLwW6n4Sf3hILlTzkjJKUaDBdHI0PHgGpO1fzK4lLVYCegU0WeU7WiuhYDB2Sfke7S8TdQ\",\"signingKeySignature\":\"0x76c8c422e0e15970215a841410414e82c1edfe8effdb87fea3c811942b3ea78c6242662f21a41f700fea79382bcbeac290be97549242af92f4bc2da4d685d0611c\",\"signingKeyMessage\":\"I authorize publishing on mirror.xyz from this device using:\\n{\\\"crv\\\":\\\"P-256\\\",\\\"ext\\\":true,\\\"key_ops\\\":[\\\"verify\\\"],\\\"kty\\\":\\\"EC\\\",\\\"x\\\":\\\"u1VTImaW42qZKYpTJCQc4JA6fFXOaU2iLQWK3ZuKlgs\\\",\\\"y\\\":\\\"cuS7q84y97hQVjZ8AhvNSlQ0X71TfqSzMcaGIVqzLDo\\\"}\",\"algorithm\":{\"name\":\"ECDSA\",\"hash\":\"SHA-256\"}},\"nft\":{},\"version\":\"12-21-2020\",\"originalDigest\":\"lZZpyIe-NUfc94xxS5LsPXYRb0KCK7u3mE5MUigEFLQ\"}"